# Requests Module Rules

## Request Entity

Request for service from buyer.

## Request Fields

- `id` - Unique identifier
- `title` - Request title
- `description` - Detailed description
- `category` - Category (Electronics, Design, Education, etc.)
- `budgetMin` - Minimum budget (UAH)
- `budgetMax` - Maximum budget (UAH)
- `location` - Location (city or "Remote")
- `urgency` - Urgency (Flexible, Within a week, 2-3 days, Urgent)
- `buyerId` - Buyer ID (foreign key to User)
- `images` - Array of image URLs
- `views` - Number of views
- `proposalsCount` - Number of proposals
- `status` - Status (pending, active, closed, rejected)
- `edits` - Array of edit history (text, timestamp)

## Request Statuses

- `pending` - Awaiting moderation
- `active` - Active and visible to sellers
- `closed` - Closed (proposal accepted)
- `rejected` - Rejected by admin

## Request Endpoints

- `GET /api/requests` - Get list of requests (with pagination and filters)
- `GET /api/requests/:id` - Get request details
- `POST /api/requests` - Create request (buyer only)
- `PATCH /api/requests/:id` - Update request (owner only)
- `DELETE /api/requests/:id` - Delete request (owner only)
- `GET /api/requests/:id/proposals` - Get proposals for request
- `GET /api/requests/:id/discussions` - Get discussions for request
- `POST /api/requests/:id/discussions` - Add comment to request
- `POST /api/requests/:id/report` - Report request

## Request Service

- Create request with status `pending`
- Award +10 XP to buyer on creation
- Increment view count on view
- Update proposals count when proposal is created
- Handle request status changes
- Filter and search requests
- Support pagination

## Business Logic

1. **Creation flow:**
   - Buyer creates request → status `pending`
   - Admin moderates → status `active` or `rejected`
   - When active, sellers can see and send proposals

2. **Accepting proposal:**
   - When proposal is accepted → request status becomes `closed`
   - All other proposals are rejected

## Validation

- Title: min 1 character
- Description: min 10 characters
- Budget: min >= 0, max >= min
- Category: must be valid category
- Images: max 5 images, max 10MB each
